Fred McCarren https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_McCarren 0 Frederick West "Fred" McCarren (April 12, 1951 – July 2, 2006) was an American television and film actor. He gained recognition for his roles on the television series Amanda's (1983) and Hill Street Blues (1984).
